window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A captivating story about finding your soul mates in a world fought with unseen dangers, <i>Variant Lost</i> is an Amazon top 100 best seller!</p> <p>One ordinary woman. Four extraordinary men. A power that could ruin them all.</p> <p>Driven by a promise to keep her identity secret, tenacious Evelyn Maynard is all alone in the world. But a scholarship to the exclusive Bradford Hills Institute offers her a safe haven and a fresh start. Or so she thought. Eve is one of the only humans at her new school, brimming with those born with Variant DNA—and coveted superhuman abilities.</p> <p>Bound by shared tragedy, Ethan, Josh, Tyler, and Alec—and their unique powers—are revered among Variants. But something has always been missing, and she may have just arrived with a scholarship and a glint in her enchanting, curious eyes.</p> <p>Together, they could be unimaginably powerful, but being bonded by the Light itself isn’t always a blessing, and Eve’s dangerous past could curse them all.</p> <p>Because she’s not the only one keeping secrets....</p> <p>Can they learn to trust each other in time to save themselves from an insidious danger no one saw coming?</p>"; 
